dc_title_s: City map, central Tokyo : corrected to May 1951
dc_description_s: Map shows buildings indexed, three classes of roads, military installations, military routes, dependent houses, ku boundary, and principal streets in the Tokyo area. Army control facilities are located. In lower right margin: "64th ENGR BASE TOPO BN - BN 2902 - 6/51 - 25M." Indexes, text, and mileage chart of Honshu on verso. On verso: Marunouchi District -- Approaches to Tokyo (1:625,000).
dc_creator_sm: United States. Army. Engineer Base Topographic Battalion, 64th
dc_publisher_s: Tokyo : Office of the Engineer, GHQ, FEC, [June], 1951.
